Interface SparseVectorMixin<T extends SparseVectorMixin<T,U,V,W,X,Y>,U extends DenseVectorMixin<U,T,W,X,Y>,V extends CooMatrixMixin<V,W,T,U,X,Y>,W extends DenseMatrixMixinOld<W,V,U,X,Y>,X,Y>

Type Parameters:
T - Type of this sparse vector.
U - Type of equivalent dense vector.
V - Type of matrix equivalent to T.
W - Type of dense matrix equivalent to V.
Y - Type (or wrapper of) an individual element in this vector.
